{
  "video_id": "pgmiPXAwiLg",
  "title": "My failed mission to find God -- and what I found instead | Anjali Kumar",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13300.0,
      "end_time": 14475.0,
      "text": "A few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14499.0,
      "end_time": 17458.0,
      "text": "I set out on a mission to find God."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17985.0,
      "end_time": 20649.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m going to tell you right up front that I failed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20673.0,
      "end_time": 22258.0,
      "text": "which, as a lawyer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22283.0,
      "end_time": 24440.0,
      "text": "is a really hard thing for me to admit."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25194.0,
      "end_time": 27774.0,
      "text": "But on that failed journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27798.0,
      "end_time": 30227.0,
      "text": "a lot of what I found was enlightening."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30873.0,
      "end_time": 33801.0,
      "text": "And one thing in particular gave me a lot of hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34378.0,
      "end_time": 38304.0,
      "text": "It has to do with the magnitude and significance of our differences."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39616.0,
      "end_time": 43441.0,
      "text": "So, I was raised in America by Indian parents -- culturally Hindu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43465.0,
      "end_time": 47807.0,
      "text": "but practicing a strict and relatively unknown religion outside of India"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47831.0,
      "end_time": 48987.0,
      "text": "called Jainism."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49610.0,
      "end_time": 52559.0,
      "text": "To give you an idea of just how minority that makes me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53233.0,
      "end_time": 57507.0,
      "text": "people from India represent roughly one percent of the US population;"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57973.0,
      "end_time": 60159.0,
      "text": "Hindus, about 0.7 percent;"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60667.0,
      "end_time": 66965.0,
      "text": "Jains, at most .00046 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67557.0,
      "end_time": 69122.0,
      "text": "To put that in context:"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69513.0,
      "end_time": 72692.0,
      "text": "more people visit the Vermont Teddy Bear Factory each year"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72716.0,
      "end_time": 75431.0,
      "text": "than are followers of the Jain religion in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75455.0,
      "end_time": 78356.0,
      "text": "To add to my minority mix, my parents then decided,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78380.0,
      "end_time": 81740.0,
      "text": "\"What a great idea! Let&#39;s send her to Catholic school\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81980.0,
      "end_time": 82116.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82140.0,
      "end_time": 84319.0,
      "text": "where my sister and I were the only non-white,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84343.0,
      "end_time": 86700.0,
      "text": "non-Catholic students in the entire school."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87287.0,
      "end_time": 91611.0,
      "text": "At the Infant Jesus of Prague School in Flossmoor, Illinois --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91635.0,
      "end_time": 94107.0,
      "text": "yes, that&#39;s really what it was called --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94131.0,
      "end_time": 97815.0,
      "text": "we were taught to believe that there is a single Supreme Being"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97839.0,
      "end_time": 100470.0,
      "text": "who is responsible for everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100710.0,
      "end_time": 101301.0,
      "text": "the whole shebang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101325.0,
      "end_time": 105481.0,
      "text": "from the creation of the Universe to moral shepherding to eternal life."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106230.0,
      "end_time": 107173.0,
      "text": "But at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107198.0,
      "end_time": 109967.0,
      "text": "I was being taught something entirely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110780.0,
      "end_time": 112461.0,
      "text": "Followers of the Jain religion"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112485.0,
      "end_time": 114594.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t believe in a single Supreme Being"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114618.0,
      "end_time": 116398.0,
      "text": "or even a team of Supreme Beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116747.0,
      "end_time": 118786.0,
      "text": "Instead, we&#39;re taught that God manifests"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118810.0,
      "end_time": 121812.0,
      "text": "as the perfection of each of us as individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121836.0,
      "end_time": 124320.0,
      "text": "and that we&#39;re actually spending our entire lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124344.0,
      "end_time": 126223.0,
      "text": "striving to remove the bad karmas"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 126247.0,
      "end_time": 130559.0,
      "text": "that stand in the way of us becoming our own godlike, perfect selves."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131329.0,
      "end_time": 134617.0,
      "text": "On top of that, one of the core principles of Jainism"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134641.0,
      "end_time": 137286.0,
      "text": "is something called \"non-absolutism.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137771.0,
      "end_time": 140726.0,
      "text": "Non-absolutists believe that no single person"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140751.0,
      "end_time": 144256.0,
      "text": "can hold ownership or knowledge of absolute truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144875.0,
      "end_time": 147232.0,
      "text": "even when it comes to religious beliefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148169.0,
      "end_time": 150114.0,
      "text": "Good luck testing that concept out"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150138.0,
      "end_time": 152569.0,
      "text": "on the priests and nuns in your Catholic school."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152593.0,
      "end_time": 153909.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153933.0,
      "end_time": 155709.0,
      "text": "No wonder I was confused"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155734.0,
      "end_time": 159290.0,
      "text": "and hyperaware of how different I was from my peers."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159893.0,
      "end_time": 161843.0,
      "text": "Cut to 20-something years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161867.0,
      "end_time": 164750.0,
      "text": "and I found myself to be a highly spiritual person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164774.0,
      "end_time": 166328.0,
      "text": "but I was floundering."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166352.0,
      "end_time": 167982.0,
      "text": "I was spiritually homeless."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 168633.0,
      "end_time": 171812.0,
      "text": "I came to learn that I was a \"None,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171836.0,
      "end_time": 174974.0,
      "text": "which isn&#39;t an acronym or a clever play on words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174998.0,
      "end_time": 177430.0,
      "text": "nor is it one of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177663.0,
      "end_time": 180377.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s simply the painfully uninspired name"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 180401.0,
      "end_time": 184144.0,
      "text": "given to everyone who checks off the box \"none\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184168.0,
      "end_time": 187516.0,
      "text": "when Pew Research asks them about their religious affiliation."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 187540.0,
      "end_time": 188564.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 188588.0,
      "end_time": 191570.0,
      "text": "Now, a couple of interesting things about Nones are:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191810.0,
      "end_time": 192262.0,
      "text": "there are a lot of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192287.0,
      "end_time": 193773.0,
      "text": "and we skew young."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194948.0,
      "end_time": 201286.0,
      "text": "In 2014, there were over 56 million religiously unaffiliated Nones"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201310.0,
      "end_time": 202487.0,
      "text": "in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203290.0,
      "end_time": 207165.0,
      "text": "And Nones account for over one-third of adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207189.0,
      "end_time": 209951.0,
      "text": "between the ages of 18 to 33."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210489.0,
      "end_time": 213442.0,
      "text": "But the most interesting thing to me about Nones"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213466.0,
      "end_time": 215768.0,
      "text": "is that we&#39;re often spiritual."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215792.0,
      "end_time": 220120.0,
      "text": "In fact, 68 percent of us believe, with some degree of certainty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220360.0,
      "end_time": 221416.0,
      "text": "that there is a God."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 221440.0,
      "end_time": 222953.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re just not sure who it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222977.0,
      "end_time": 224977.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 225861.0,
      "end_time": 227826.0,
      "text": "So the first takeaway for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227850.0,
      "end_time": 231911.0,
      "text": "when I realized I was a None and had found that information out"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 231935.0,
      "end_time": 233743.0,
      "text": "was that I wasn&#39;t alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234139.0,
      "end_time": 236179.0,
      "text": "I was finally part of a group in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236203.0,
      "end_time": 237681.0,
      "text": "that had a lot of members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 237705.0,
      "end_time": 239340.0,
      "text": "which felt really reassuring."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 239731.0,
      "end_time": 242422.0,
      "text": "But then the second, not-so-reassuring takeaway"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 242446.0,
      "end_time": 244677.0,
      "text": "was that, oh, man, there are a lot of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 244701.0,
      "end_time": 245923.0,
      "text": "That can&#39;t be good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245947.0,
      "end_time": 249800.0,
      "text": "because if a lot of highly spiritual people are currently godless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 249824.0,
      "end_time": 253559.0,
      "text": "maybe finding God is not going to be as easy as I had originally hoped."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253583.0,
      "end_time": 256906.0,
      "text": "So that is when I decided that on my spiritual journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 256930.0,
      "end_time": 259500.0,
      "text": "I was going to avoid the obvious places"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259290.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261524.00000000003,
      "text": "and skip the big-box religions altogether"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261548.0,
      "end_time": 265207.0,
      "text": "and instead venture out into the spiritual fringe"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265231.0,
      "end_time": 266540.0,
      "text": "of mediums"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 266564.0,
      "end_time": 267746.0,
      "text": "and faith healers"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 268381.0,
      "end_time": 269542.0,
      "text": "and godmen."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 270336.0,
      "end_time": 272374.0,
      "text": "But remember, I&#39;m a non-absolutist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 272398.0,
      "end_time": 276317.0,
      "text": "which means I was pretty inclined to keep a fairly open mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 276341.0,
      "end_time": 278429.0,
      "text": "which turned out to be a good thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 278453.0,
      "end_time": 282167.0,
      "text": "because I went to a witch&#39;s potluck dinner"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 282191.0,
      "end_time": 285102.0,
      "text": "at the LGBT Center in New York City,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 285127.0,
      "end_time": 286839.0,
      "text": "where I befriended two witches;"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287814.0,
      "end_time": 291555.0,
      "text": "drank a five-gallon jerrican full of volcanic water"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 291579.0,
      "end_time": 292959.0,
      "text": "with a shaman in Peru;"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 294173.0,
      "end_time": 296593.0,
      "text": "got a hug from a saint in the convention center --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 296617.0,
      "end_time": 297962.0,
      "text": "she smelled really nice --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 297986.0,
      "end_time": 299715.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 299739.0,
      "end_time": 303486.0,
      "text": "chanted for hours in a smoke-filled, heat-infused sweat lodge"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 303510.0,
      "end_time": 304997.0,
      "text": "on the beaches of Mexico;"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 305958.0,
      "end_time": 309246.0,
      "text": "worked with a tequila-drinking medium to convene with the dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 309270.0,
      "end_time": 312628.0,
      "text": "who oddly included both my deceased mother-in-law"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 312652.0,
      "end_time": 315828.0,
      "text": "and the deceased manager of the hip-hop group The Roots."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 315852.0,
      "end_time": 316935.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 316959.0,
      "end_time": 319702.0,
      "text": "Yeah, my mother-in-law told me she was really happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 319726.0,
      "end_time": 321732.0,
      "text": "her son had chosen me for his wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 321756.0,
      "end_time": 322907.0,
      "text": "Duh! But --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 322931.0,
      "end_time": 324870.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324894.0,
      "end_time": 326520.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 326760.0,
      "end_time": 328165.0,
      "text": "But the manager of The Roots"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 328189.0,
      "end_time": 331505.0,
      "text": "said that maybe I should cut back on all the pasta I was eating."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 331529.0,
      "end_time": 333137.0,
      "text": "I think we can all agree"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 333161.0,
      "end_time": 336199.0,
      "text": "that it was lucky for my husband that it wasn&#39;t his dead mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 336223.0,
      "end_time": 337706.0,
      "text": "who suggested I lay off carbs."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 337730.0,
      "end_time": 338824.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 338848.0,
      "end_time": 342727.0,
      "text": "I also joined a laughing yoga group out of South Africa;"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 343917.0,
      "end_time": 347587.0,
      "text": "witnessed a woman have a 45-minute orgasm --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 347612.0,
      "end_time": 348935.0,
      "text": "I am not making this up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 348959.0,
      "end_time": 351521.0,
      "text": "as she tapped into the energy of the universe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 351545.0,
      "end_time": 353366.0,
      "text": "I think I&#39;m going to go back there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 353844.0,
      "end_time": 356216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 357350.0,
      "end_time": 361406.0,
      "text": "called God from a phone booth in the Nevada desert at Burning Man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 361430.0,
      "end_time": 363498.0,
      "text": "wearing a unitard and ski goggles;"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 364556.0,
      "end_time": 368630.0,
      "text": "and I had an old Indian guy lie on top of me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 368880.0,
      "end_time": 370980.0,
      "text": "and no, he wasn&#39;t my husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 370122.0,
      "end_time": 372535.0,
      "text": "This was a perfect stranger named Paramji,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 372559.0,
      "end_time": 374322.0,
      "text": "and he was chanting into my chakras"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 374346.0,
      "end_time": 379240.0,
      "text": "as he tapped into the energy forces of the Universe to heal my \"yoni,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 379480.0,
      "end_time": 382390.0,
      "text": "which is a Sanskrit word for \"vagina.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 382630.0,
      "end_time": 383387.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 383411.0,
      "end_time": 384983.0,
      "text": "I was going to have a slide here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 385700.0,
      "end_time": 386838.0,
      "text": "but a few people suggested"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 386862.0,
      "end_time": 391177.0,
      "text": "that a slide of my yoni at TED -- even TEDWomen --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 391201.0,
      "end_time": 392560.0,
      "text": "not the best idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 392584.0,
      "end_time": 393742.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 394927.0,
      "end_time": 396591.0,
      "text": "Very early in my quest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 396615.0,
      "end_time": 399951.0,
      "text": "I also went to see the Brazilian faith healer John of God"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 399975.0,
      "end_time": 401740.0,
      "text": "at his compound down in Brazil."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 402166.0,
      "end_time": 405215.0,
      "text": "Now, John of God is considered a full-trance medium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 405239.0,
      "end_time": 407760.0,
      "text": "which basically means he can talk to dead people."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 408173.0,
      "end_time": 411938.0,
      "text": "But in his case, he claims to channel a very specific group"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 411962.0,
      "end_time": 413400.0,
      "text": "of dead saints and doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 413424.0,
      "end_time": 415803.0,
      "text": "in order to heal whatever&#39;s wrong with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 415827.0,
      "end_time": 418775.0,
      "text": "And although John of God does not have a medical degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 418799.0,
      "end_time": 420883.0,
      "text": "or even a high school diploma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 421653.0,
      "end_time": 423352.0,
      "text": "he actually performs surgery --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 424186.0,
      "end_time": 425861.0,
      "text": "the real kind, with a scalpel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 426504.0,
      "end_time": 427741.0,
      "text": "but no anesthesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 428893.0,
      "end_time": 430530.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 430770.0,
      "end_time": 433547.0,
      "text": "He also offers invisible surgery, where there is no cutting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 433571.0,
      "end_time": 434728.0,
      "text": "and surrogate surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 434752.0,
      "end_time": 438850.0,
      "text": "where he supposedly can treat somebody who is thousands of miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 438874.0,
      "end_time": 441760.0,
      "text": "by performing a procedure on a loved one."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 441747.0,
      "end_time": 443590.0,
      "text": "Now, when you go to visit John of God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 443614.0,
      "end_time": 445750.0,
      "text": "there are all kinds of rules and regulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 445774.0,
      "end_time": 447356.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a whole complicated thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 447380.0,
      "end_time": 450639.0,
      "text": "but the bottom line is that you can visit John of God"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 450663.0,
      "end_time": 453870.0,
      "text": "and present him with three things that you would like fixed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 453894.0,
      "end_time": 456991.0,
      "text": "and he will set the dead saints and doctors to work on your behalf"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 457150.0,
      "end_time": 458198.0,
      "text": "to get the job done."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 458222.0,
      "end_time": 459231.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 459255.0,
      "end_time": 461730.0,
      "text": "Now, before you snicker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 461754.0,
      "end_time": 463238.0,
      "text": "consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 463262.0,
      "end_time": 465234.0,
      "text": "that, at least according to his website,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 465258.0,
      "end_time": 467390.0,
      "text": "over eight million people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 467802.0,
      "end_time": 468980.0,
      "text": "including Oprah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 469630.0,
      "end_time": 471575.0,
      "text": "the Goddess of Daytime TV --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 472441.0,
      "end_time": 474304.0,
      "text": "have gone to see John of God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 474328.0,
      "end_time": 476991.0,
      "text": "and I was pre-wired to keep an open mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 478124.0,
      "end_time": 481742.0,
      "text": "But to be honest, the whole thing for me was kind of weird and inconclusive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 481766.0,
      "end_time": 483517.0,
      "text": "and in the end, I flew home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 483541.0,
      "end_time": 486320.0,
      "text": "even more confused than I already started out."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 486913.0,
      "end_time": 489295.0,
      "text": "But that doesn&#39;t mean I came home empty-handed."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 490605.0,
      "end_time": 493158.0,
      "text": "In the weeks leading up to my trip to Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 493182.0,
      "end_time": 495951.0,
      "text": "I mentioned my upcoming plans to some friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 495975.0,
      "end_time": 497921.0,
      "text": "and to a couple of colleagues at Google,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 497945.0,
      "end_time": 499616.0,
      "text": "where I was a lawyer at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 500280.0,
      "end_time": 502536.0,
      "text": "And I might have mentioned it to a couple more people"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 502560.0,
      "end_time": 503751.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m chatty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 503775.0,
      "end_time": 504983.0,
      "text": "including my neighbor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 505672.0,
      "end_time": 508768.0,
      "text": "the guy who works at the local coffee shop I go to each morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 509181.0,
      "end_time": 510914.0,
      "text": "the checkout lady at Whole Foods"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 511486.0,
      "end_time": 513822.0,
      "text": "and a stranger who sat next to me on the subway."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 514743.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516959.00000000006,
      "text": "I told each of them where I was going"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 516982.0,
      "end_time": 518154.0,
      "text": "and why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 518178.0,
      "end_time": 522599.0,
      "text": "and I offered to carry three wishes of theirs down to Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 522623.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525392.0,
      "text": "explaining that anyone going to see John of God"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 525416.0,
      "end_time": 527226.0,
      "text": "could act as a proxy for others"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 527250.0,
      "end_time": 528422.0,
      "text": "and save them the trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 529795.0,
      "end_time": 532930.0,
      "text": "And to my surprise, my in-box overflowed."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 533906.0,
      "end_time": 535806.0,
      "text": "Friends told friends who told friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 535831.0,
      "end_time": 538670.0,
      "text": "and those friends apparently told more friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 538910.0,
      "end_time": 540501.0,
      "text": "other strangers and the guys at their coffee shops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 540525.0,
      "end_time": 542929.0,
      "text": "until it seemed that days before I left for Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 542953.0,
      "end_time": 545887.0,
      "text": "that there was no one who did not have my email address."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 546765.0,
      "end_time": 551115.0,
      "text": "And at the time, all I could conclude was that I had offered too much"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 551139.0,
      "end_time": 552296.0,
      "text": "to too many."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 553302.0,
      "end_time": 556981.0,
      "text": "But when I actually reread those messages a few years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 558172.0,
      "end_time": 560937.0,
      "text": "I noticed something completely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 562728.0,
      "end_time": 566510.0,
      "text": "Those emails actually shared three commonalities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 566885.0,
      "end_time": 568709.0,
      "text": "the first of which was rather curious."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 569791.0,
      "end_time": 574431.0,
      "text": "Almost everyone sent me meticulous details about how they could be reached."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 575239.0,
      "end_time": 578135.0,
      "text": "I had told them, or their friends had told them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 578159.0,
      "end_time": 581292.0,
      "text": "that along with the list of the three things they wanted fixed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 581316.0,
      "end_time": 584914.0,
      "text": "I needed their photo, their name and their date of birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 585533.0,
      "end_time": 589665.0,
      "text": "But they gave me full addresses, with, like, apartment numbers and zip codes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 589689.0,
      "end_time": 592440.0,
      "text": "as if John of God was going to stop by their house"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 592680.0,
      "end_time": 594420.0,
      "text": "and see them in person or send along a package."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 595250.0,
      "end_time": 599607.0,
      "text": "It was as if, in the highly unlikely event that their wishes were granted"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 599631.0,
      "end_time": 600823.0,
      "text": "by John of God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 600847.0,
      "end_time": 603620.0,
      "text": "they just wanted to make sure that they weren&#39;t delivered"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 603644.0,
      "end_time": 605614.0,
      "text": "to the wrong person or the wrong address."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 605638.0,
      "end_time": 607804.0,
      "text": "Even if they didn&#39;t believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 607828.0,
      "end_time": 609432.0,
      "text": "they were hedging their bets."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 610785.0,
      "end_time": 613698.0,
      "text": "The second commonality was just as curious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 614612.0,
      "end_time": 615997.0,
      "text": "but far more humbling."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 617784.0,
      "end_time": 619145.0,
      "text": "Virtually everyone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 619925.0,
      "end_time": 621229.0,
      "text": "the stranger on the subway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 621827.0,
      "end_time": 623135.0,
      "text": "the guy at the coffee shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 623530.0,
      "end_time": 624853.0,
      "text": "the lawyer down the hall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 625310.0,
      "end_time": 628482.0,
      "text": "the Jew, the atheist, the Muslim, the devout Catholic --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 628873.0,
      "end_time": 632850.0,
      "text": "all asked for essentially the same three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 633200.0,
      "end_time": 636687.0,
      "text": "OK, there were a couple of outliers, and yes, a few people asked for cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 636711.0,
      "end_time": 641930.0,
      "text": "But when I eliminated what were ultimately a handful of anomalies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 641527.0,
      "end_time": 643841.0,
      "text": "the similarities were staggering."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 645931.0,
      "end_time": 648119.0,
      "text": "Almost every single person"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 648828.0,
      "end_time": 652667.0,
      "text": "first asked for good health for themselves and their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 654100.0,
      "end_time": 655377.0,
      "text": "Almost universally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 656212.0,
      "end_time": 657686.0,
      "text": "they next asked for happiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 658829.0,
      "end_time": 659979.0,
      "text": "and then love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 661439.0,
      "end_time": 662615.0,
      "text": "in that order:"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 663824.0,
      "end_time": 665579.0,
      "text": "health, happiness, love."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 667585.0,
      "end_time": 670512.0,
      "text": "Sometimes they asked for a specific health issue to be fixed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 670536.0,
      "end_time": 673858.0,
      "text": "but more often than not, they just asked for good health in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 675222.0,
      "end_time": 676497.0,
      "text": "When it came to happiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 677310.0,
      "end_time": 679207.0,
      "text": "they each phrased it slightly differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 680520.0,
      "end_time": 684648.0,
      "text": "but they all asked for the same specific subtype of happiness, too --"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 686282.0,
      "end_time": 688363.0,
      "text": "the kind of happiness that sinks in"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 688832.0,
      "end_time": 690775.0,
      "text": "and sets down roots in your soul;"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 692521.0,
      "end_time": 694857.0,
      "text": "the kind of happiness that could sustain us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 695922.0,
      "end_time": 698848.0,
      "text": "even if we were to lose absolutely everything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 700587.0,
      "end_time": 701739.0,
      "text": "And for love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 702779.0,
      "end_time": 704997.0,
      "text": "they all asked for the kind of romantic love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 705210.0,
      "end_time": 708997.0,
      "text": "the soul mate that we read about in epic romantic novels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 710396.0,
      "end_time": 713616.0,
      "text": "the kind of love that will stay with us till the end of our days."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 715893.0,
      "end_time": 717908.0,
      "text": "Sorry, that&#39;s my husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 720665.0,
      "end_time": 722250.0,
      "text": "Crap! Now I forgot my place."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 722274.0,
      "end_time": 724293.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 725176.0,
      "end_time": 729977.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 734602.0,
      "end_time": 736161.0,
      "text": "So by and large,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 736185.0,
      "end_time": 738573.0,
      "text": "all of these friends and strangers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 738597.0,
      "end_time": 741951.0,
      "text": "regardless of their background, race or religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 742762.0,
      "end_time": 744425.0,
      "text": "all asked for the same things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 744450.0,
      "end_time": 747212.0,
      "text": "and they were the same things that I really wanted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 747236.0,
      "end_time": 750380.0,
      "text": "the simplified version of the basic human needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 750620.0,
      "end_time": 754683.0,
      "text": "identified by social scientists like Abraham Maslow and Manfred Max-Neef."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 755668.0,
      "end_time": 758786.0,
      "text": "No one asked for answers to the big existential questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 758810.0,
      "end_time": 762214.0,
      "text": "or for proof of God or the meaning of life like I had set out to find."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 762596.0,
      "end_time": 765578.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t even ask for an end to war or global hunger."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 766879.0,
      "end_time": 770482.0,
      "text": "Even when they could have asked for absolutely anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 770506.0,
      "end_time": 773540.0,
      "text": "they all asked for health, happiness and love."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 775418.0,
      "end_time": 778166.0,
      "text": "So now those emails had a third commonality as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 779444.0,
      "end_time": 782572.0,
      "text": "Each of them ended in the exact same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 783597.0,
      "end_time": 787363.0,
      "text": "Instead of thanking me for carting their wishes all the way to Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 788427.0,
      "end_time": 789642.0,
      "text": "everyone said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 791285.0,
      "end_time": 792757.0,
      "text": "\"Please don&#39;t tell anyone.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 794738.0,
      "end_time": 796954.0,
      "text": "So I decided to tell everyone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 796978.0,
      "end_time": 798209.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 798233.0,
      "end_time": 799731.0,
      "text": "right here on this stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 801421.0,
      "end_time": 803211.0,
      "text": "not because I&#39;m untrustworthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 803867.0,
      "end_time": 807108.0,
      "text": "but because the fact that we have so much in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 807133.0,
      "end_time": 810619.0,
      "text": "feels especially important for us all to hear, especially now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 810643.0,
      "end_time": 812690.0,
      "text": "when so many of the world&#39;s problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 812714.0,
      "end_time": 816701.0,
      "text": "seem to be because we keep focusing on the things that make us different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 816725.0,
      "end_time": 818608.0,
      "text": "not on what binds us together."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 819765.0,
      "end_time": 824141.0,
      "text": "And look -- I am the first to admit that I am not a statistician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 824790.0,
      "end_time": 828709.0,
      "text": "and that the data I presented to you that I just accumulated in my in-box"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 828734.0,
      "end_time": 833835.0,
      "text": "is more anecdotal than scientific, more qualitative than quantitative."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 834394.0,
      "end_time": 837616.0,
      "text": "It is, as anyone who works with data would tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 837640.0,
      "end_time": 841464.0,
      "text": "hardly a statistically significant or demographically balanced sample."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 841488.0,
      "end_time": 845549.0,
      "text": "But nonetheless, I find myself thinking about those emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 845573.0,
      "end_time": 849125.0,
      "text": "every time I reflect back on the bias and prejudice"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 849149.0,
      "end_time": 850666.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve faced in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 851131.0,
      "end_time": 854250.0,
      "text": "or when there&#39;s another hate crime or a senseless tragedy"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 854490.0,
      "end_time": 856661.0,
      "text": "that underscores the disheartening sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 856685.0,
      "end_time": 859537.0,
      "text": "that our differences might be insurmountable."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 861700.0,
      "end_time": 863380.0,
      "text": "I then remind myself that I have evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 863404.0,
      "end_time": 865986.0,
      "text": "that the humbling, unifying commonality"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 866100.0,
      "end_time": 867620.0,
      "text": "of our humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 867644.0,
      "end_time": 870612.0,
      "text": "is that, even when presented with the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 870636.0,
      "end_time": 872789.0,
      "text": "to ask for anything at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 872813.0,
      "end_time": 874750.0,
      "text": "most of us want the same things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 874774.0,
      "end_time": 877479.0,
      "text": "and that this is true no matter who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 878179.0,
      "end_time": 880960.0,
      "text": "what name we call our god,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 880702.0,
      "end_time": 883824.0,
      "text": "or which religion, if any, we call home."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 885300.0,
      "end_time": 886904.0,
      "text": "I then also note"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 886928.0,
      "end_time": 890295.0,
      "text": "that apparently some of us want these things so badly"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 890821.0,
      "end_time": 892598.0,
      "text": "that we would email a None,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 893319.0,
      "end_time": 896606.0,
      "text": "a spiritually confused None like me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 896630.0,
      "end_time": 898738.0,
      "text": "some might say otherwise confused as well --"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 899742.0,
      "end_time": 904522.0,
      "text": "and that we would seek out this stranger and email her our deepest wishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 904547.0,
      "end_time": 907892.0,
      "text": "just in case there is the remote possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 907916.0,
      "end_time": 911557.0,
      "text": "that they might be granted by someone who is not a god,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 911581.0,
      "end_time": 913970.0,
      "text": "much less our god,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 913994.0,
      "end_time": 916967.0,
      "text": "someone who is not even a member of our chosen religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 917998.0,
      "end_time": 919999.0,
      "text": "someone who, when you look at him on paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 920230.0,
      "end_time": 922513.0,
      "text": "seems like an unlikely candidate to deliver."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 924354.0,
      "end_time": 925519.0,
      "text": "And so now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 926494.0,
      "end_time": 929623.0,
      "text": "when I reflect back on my spiritual quest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 931758.0,
      "end_time": 933878.0,
      "text": "even though I did not find God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 935211.0,
      "end_time": 937519.0,
      "text": "I found a home in this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 939170.0,
      "end_time": 943290.0,
      "text": "even today, in a world fractured by religious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 944690.0,
      "end_time": 949205.0,
      "text": "ethnic, political, philosophical, and racial divides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 949230.0,
      "end_time": 952264.0,
      "text": "even with all of our obvious differences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 952288.0,
      "end_time": 953703.0,
      "text": "at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 954311.0,
      "end_time": 956260.0,
      "text": "and the most fundamental level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 956886.0,
      "end_time": 958280.0,
      "text": "we are all the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 959613.0,
      "end_time": 960776.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 960800.0,
      "end_time": 966413.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}